{"title":"吃喝风再起","authors":["江帆","池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":1,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃喝风再起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江帆画  池北偶诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据报载，前一个时期由于明令禁止，利用公费吃喝之风稍敛，最近有些地方又有重新抬头之势。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公费宴会是惯经，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碍于禁令稍消停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并非一时无胃口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是为了避风声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今风头已渐过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重开筵席互相请。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八菜两汤算廉政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃喝也是为革命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"川鲁风味、孔府宴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正宗粤菜、美食城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干白、啤酒、白兰地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茅台、特曲、竹叶青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡、鸭、鱼、肉吃腻了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝尝鹿脯与蛇羹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放开肚皮吃个够，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帐由会计去付清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}